Isotropy everywhere implies homogeneity.

2112
01:19:11,220 --> 01:19:12,160
In other words,

2113
01:19:12,280 --> 01:19:13,520
isotropy is homogeneous.

2114
01:19:14,340 --> 01:19:15,380
In other words,

2115
01:19:15,380 --> 01:19:16,440
isotropy is homogeneous.

2116
01:19:16,960 --> 01:19:17,340
Yeah.

2117
01:19:18,180 --> 01:19:20,500
If the universe is not homogeneous,

2118
01:19:21,020 --> 01:19:22,560
