2122
01:19:32,460 --> 01:19:32,920
No,

2123
01:19:32,920 --> 01:19:33,060
no.

2124
01:19:33,120 --> 01:19:33,540
That's right.

2125
01:19:33,660 --> 01:19:34,120
That's right.

