2139
01:19:57,920 --> 01:19:59,700
It has a direction associated with it.

2140
01:19:59,820 --> 01:20:00,100
Right.

2141
01:20:04,400 --> 01:20:07,240
And isotropy doesn't imply homogeneity.

2142
