01:20:52,560 --> 01:20:52,840
Every direction is the same

2168
01:20:52,840 --> 01:20:53,740
as every other place.

2169
01:20:54,599 --> 01:20:56,500
Every direction that you look in

2170
01:20:56,500 --> 01:20:58,140
