01:21:31,640 --> 01:21:33,020
If light only travels

2195
01:21:33,020 --> 01:21:34,200
on the surface of the sphere,

2196
01:21:34,340 --> 01:21:35,940
all they can do is look around

2197
01:21:35,940 --> 01:21:37,540
