01:22:05,120 --> 01:22:07,120
So boundedness does not mean boundary.

2217
01:22:07,300 --> 01:22:11,540
It means boundedness.

2218
01:22:13,780 --> 01:22:14,920
Finiteness in some sense,

2219
01:22:14,920 --> 01:22:15,120
