01:23:14,140 --> 01:23:15,580
Left and right being the same.

2254
01:23:15,760 --> 01:23:16,240
That's right.

2255
01:23:16,400 --> 01:23:17,600
So here,

2256
01:23:17,600 --> 01:23:18,260
for example,

2257
01:23:18,420 --> 01:23:19,920
is a one-dimensional world

