01:24:05,600 --> 01:24:07,580
And I would say this was homogeneous,

2282
01:24:09,779 --> 01:24:10,379
isotropic,

2283
01:24:10,379 --> 01:24:11,480
and bounded.

2284
01:24:12,500 --> 01:24:13,100
Okay.

